snippet.title: Ynglet - Prologue
snippet.description:
Steam Description:

Ynglet: Prologue presents the first levels of my new game Ynglet! You’ll jump between bubbles that float in the sky like you’re a space dolphin, as you melt into a highly reactive and dynamic soundtrack created by Ynglet’s custom (and needlessly complicated) music software!

https://store.steampowered.com/app/1336070/Ynglet_Prologue/
